<p><strong>Skills</strong> Animal Handling +2, Athletics +5, Deception +4, Persuasion +4</p>

<p><strong>Languages</strong> Auran, Common</p>

<p><strong>Challenge</strong> 3 (700 XP)</p>

<p><strong><em>Spellcasting.</em></strong> Thurl is a 5th-level spellcaster. His spellcasting ability is Charisma (spell save DC 12, +4 to hit with spell attacks). Thurl knows the following sorcerer spells:</p>

<ul>
  <li>
    <p>Cantrips (at will): friends, gust, light, message, ray of frost</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>1st level (4 slots): expeditious retreat, feather fall, jump</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>2nd level (3 slots): levitate, misty step</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>3rd level (2 slots): haste</p>
  </li>
</ul>

<p><strong>Actions</strong></p>

<p><strong><em>Multiattack.</em></strong> Thurl makes two melee attacks.</p>

<p><strong><em>Greatsword.</em></strong> Melee Weapon Attack: +5 to hit, reach 5 ft., one target. Hit: 10 (2d6 + 3) slashing damage.</p>

<p><strong><em>Lance.</em></strong> Melee Weapon Attack: +5 to hit, reach 10 ft., one target. Hit: 9 (1d12 + 3) piercing damage.</p>

<p><strong>Reactions</strong></p>

<p><strong><em>Parry.</em></strong> Thurl adds 2 to his AC against one melee attack that would hit him. To do so, Thurl must see the attacker and be wielding a melee weapon.</p>

